attributes.name: circuits
attributes.doc: Circuits defined as lists of operations. Each list is a circuit that uses Automatic Quantum Circuit Encoding to embed an image in the complex amplitudes of a quantum state.

attributes.name: target_states
attributes.doc: A list of numpy arrays. Each numpy array defines a quantum state that exactly encodes an MNIST image.

attributes.name: labels
attributes.doc: A list of the correct labels for each image.

attributes.name: fidelity
attributes.doc: The fidelity between the target state and the state implemented by the circuit.
